GAL16V8
SparsePTD

Clock I0    I1    I2    I3    NC    NC    NC    NC   GND
/OE   NC    NC    O3    O2    O1    O0    NC    NC   VCC

O0 = I0

O1 = I0 * I1 + /I0 * /I1

O2 = I2 + I3

O3 = I0 * I1 * I2 * I3

DESCRIPTION

Sparse GAL16V8 design used to exercise PTD bit emission. O0 uses 1 product
term, O1 uses 2, O2 uses 2, O3 uses 1. OLMC pins 12, 13, 18, 19 are unused
(four entire OLMCs with no equation), so with --ptd many PTD bits should be 0.
